guy%E1%BB%85n-Bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-Uf2ziZRvBq_18AgAoHq9Fw">Nguyễn Biểu - 阮表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-P_O0C8eAMSSE0VWCvRAM-w">Đặng Minh Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-dWrwrCMfLobY07rDQtUeng">Thuật hoài kỳ 3 - 述懷其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%E1%BA%A3o/Tr%C6%B0ng-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-UNDGiY-TKTrCYMhyPxc56g">Trưng vương đại tướng từ - 徵王大將祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%E1%BA%A3o/author-DPVGLCjZS_EgF1Yc2ZvgHw">Trần Bảo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-B%E1%BB%91-C%C3%A1i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-VXA-sHmKa7uXeTqRhWbrpw">Vịnh Bố Cái Đại Vương từ - 詠布丐大王祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/author-9ppkdEWSUlq0gOg71v0QIQ">Trần Bá Lãm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
